<td class="navbox-abovebelow" style=";" colspan="2">&#160;<span class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand" style="white-space: nowrap; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Armenian_Genocide" title="Template:Armenian Genocide">v</a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Armenian_Genocide" title="Template talk:Armenian Genocide"><span title="Discussion about this template.">d</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Armenian_Genocide&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Armenian_Genocide&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span style="color:#002bb8;" title="You can edit this template. Please use the preview button before saving.">e</span></a></span>&#160;</td>
