<li><a href="http://www.armeniapedia.org/index.php?title=Armenian_Genocide" class="external text" title="http://www.armeniapedia.org/index.php?title=Armenian_Genocide" rel="nofollow">Armenian Genocide</a> on the Armeniapedia.org website (<a href="http://www.armeniapedia.org/index.php?title=Armenian_Genocide_Photos" class="external text" title="http://www.armeniapedia.org/index.php?title=Armenian_Genocide_Photos" rel="nofollow">Wegner photos</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.theforgotten.org" class="external text" title="http://www.theforgotten.org" rel="nofollow">The Armenian Genocide</a>, at www.theforgotten.org, has videos of interviews with survivors</li>
</ul>
