1919–1921)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Polish%E2%80%93Lithuanian_War" title="Polish–Lithuanian War">Polish–Lithuanian War</a> <small>(1920)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Irish_War_of_Independence" title="Irish War of Independence">Irish War of Independence</a> <small>(1919–1921)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Turkish_War_of_Independence" title="Turkish War of Independence">Turkish War of Independence</a> including the <a href="/wiki/Greco-Turkish_War_(1919%E2%80%931922)" title="Greco-Turkish War (1919–1922)">Greco-Turkish War</a> <small>(1919–1923)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Red_Army_invasion_of_Georgia" title="Red Army invasion of Georgia">Invasion of Georgia</a> <small>(1921)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Irish_Civil_War" title="Irish Civil War">Irish Civil War</a> <small>(1922–1923)</small></div>
